奈其實更多成分是對於愛情的一種不負責任 , 一種只為了自己無憾的自私罷了。<br />\n<br />\n但是對比於用現在30多年後 , 重看這部經典老片的一點現代心境的質疑劇情上的不合理 , 有些作品的浪漫是屬於那個時代更能切身體會的情懷 . 畢竟考慮到華仔當年的社會底層角色的形象 , 以及吳倩蓮的影壇初體驗 , 兩人的青澀感反而成就了一部角色契合感十足的悲戀經典。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔係模仿早兩年嘅旺角卡門多啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2389e58c446adf33023edf0f4052919c5c97bf","tid":2369348,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2120d2933dd49b2972d4f803815fbfe96e9dc5a0","tid":2369348,"uid":317651,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得好睇過Titanic"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81837058394cc5c42255c328e42aa76a67bcfbcf","tid":2369348,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2120d2933dd49b2972d4f803815fbfe96e9dc5a0","tid":2369348,"uid":317651,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得好睇過Titanic"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}